Title: The Lost Dream
DateModified: '2019-03-08'
DatePublished: '2019-03-08'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/the-lost-dream
SetInCountry: Costa Rica
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Paula Herrera
AuthorCountry: Costa Rica
Text: My travel story begins with the ending. An adult man begins to remember what
  his days were in the place that he considered magical as a child. Time passed and
  he grew up, lost all illusion of some time returning to be this happy, but on the
  bed of his death he remembered what had happened and understood the reason of his
  life..
